            Keine Anmeldung, keine Kosten ‚Äì einfach loslegen!
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="https://creators.spotify.com/pod/show/entwicklungszeit"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white text-gray-700 font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-gray-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 text-sm"
            >
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path
                  d="M12 0C5.4 0 0 5.4 0 12s5.4 12 12 12 12-5.4 12-12S18.66 0 12 0zm5.521 17.34c-.24.359-.66.48-1.021.24-2.82-1.74-6.36-2.101-10.561-1.141-.418.122-.779-.179-.899-.539-.12-.421.18-.78.54-.9 4.56-1.021 8.52-.6 11.64 1.32.42.18.479.659.301 1.02zm1.44-3.3c-.301.42-.841.6-1.262.3-3.239-1.98-8.159-2.58-11.939-1.38-.479.12-1.02-.12-1.14-.6-.12-.48.12-1.021.6-1.141C9.6 9.9 15 10.561 18.72 12.84c.361.181.54.78.241 1.2zm.12-3.36C15.24 8.4 8.82 8.16 5.16 9.301c-.6.179-1.2-.181-1.38-.721-.18-.601.18-1.2.72-1.381 4.26-1.26 11.28-1.02 15.721 1.621.539.3.719 1.02.419 1.56-.299.421-1.02.599-1.559.3z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              Spotify
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/entwicklungszeit/id1767631664"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white text-gray-700 font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-gray-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 text-sm"
            >
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path
                  d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm0 2.182c5.423 0 9.818 4.395 9.818 9.818S17.423 21.818 12 21.818 2.182 17.423 2.182 12 6.577 2.182 12 2.182zM12 5.455c-1.807 0-3.273 1.466-3.273 3.272 0 1.807 1.466 3.273 3.273 3.273s3.273-1.466 3.273-3.273c0-1.806-1.466-3.272-3.273-3.272zm0 1.636c.903 0 1.636.733 1.636 1.636S12.903 10.364 12 10.364s-1.636-.733-1.636-1.637S11.097 7.09 12 7.09zm0 4.91c-2.168 0-3.927 1.759-3.927 3.927v5.891h1.636v-5.89c0-1.264 1.027-2.291 2.291-2.291s2.291 1.027 2.291 2.29v5.891h1.636V15.93c0-2.168-1.759-3.928-3.927-3.928z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
